nodes.text: Star Wars: Transmission is a Star Wars talk show from StarWars.com headed by Chris Hardwick, of The Nerdist fame, and Chris Gore. It was announced on the first day of Celebration VI, where the first episode was filmed. Warwick Davis was a guest. Ashley Eckstein interviewed Stephen J. Sansweet about Rancho Obi-Wan and the history of the Celebrations.
